elements.name: User is able to Login and confirm data is getting transferred from GCS to BigQuery

steps.name: Open Datafusion Project to configure pipeline
Link Source and Sink to establish connection
Enter the GCS Properties with "@TC-Demo-1_GCS" GCS bucket
Enter the BigQuery Properties for table "tableDemo"
Wait till pipeline is in running state
